This paper deals with the problem of spectrum reuse in LTE-U systems while ensuring coexistence with Wi-Fi systems. It involves analyzing interference and throughput in wireless communication systems, which falls under the categories of networked and internet-based systems (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer communication networks (cs.COM).
